==English==

===Adjective===
'''scarce''' (''comparative:'' [[scarcer]], ''superlative:'' [[scarcest]])

# [[insufficient]] to meet a [[demand]] or [[requirement]].
# [[difficult]] to find, due to [[scarcity]].

